And yes, Brad Gates spent $9,000 over three or four years on his car phone. 
That's next to nothing for a corporate CEO, many of whom manage companies that 
are smaller than the Sheriff's Department. What is he supposed to do? Waste the 
time he spends in his car? I've donated to Brad Gates for years; and as far as 
I'm concerned, I would much rather have him making calls to win support for a 
new jail, the narcotics training center at Rancho del Rio and other law 
enforcement projects. 
