<HEADLINE>
<P>
PROS AND CONS OF 'DR. GRIMES' BITTER PILL' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Regarding the very long article on Dr. Grimes, what a sad commentary on our 
civilization that such a talented and accomplished doctor is using his medical 
knowledge to extinguish life rather than save it. 
</P>
<P>
It was especially disturbing to read that the doctor and his wife couldn't 
stand to see his first hospitalized pediatric patient die, but that it doesn't 
bother them to see a life snuffed out with the use of the RU-486 pill or other 
means. 
</P>
<P>
EMMA P. COLLINS, Glendale 
</P>
