<DOCNO> LA050690-0163 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 214973 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 6, 1990, Sunday, Bulldog Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 17; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
