<P>
LANE CLOSURES PLANNED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Nighttime street repairs on Santa Monica Boulevard in West Hollywood between La 
Brea Avenue and Doheny Drive will cause lane closures for about a week starting 
Monday. The closures will last from 10:30 p.m. to 5 a.m. At least one lane will 
be open in each direction at all times. 
</P>
