ARMED FORCES -- PHILIPPINES; PHILIPPINES -- REVOLTS; CASUALTIES; GUERRILLAS -- 
PHILIPPINES; TERRORISM -- PHILIPPINES; NEW PEOPLE'S ARMY (PHILIPPINES) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
